citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"想問呢幾個月學左啲乜<br />\n樓主你似係發聲問題"},{"pid":"c5fca228ead27e426f456327634870d27f4975d2","tid":1132840,"uid":128921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"好難聽，咁低音都咁飄，你可以收得皮"},{"pid":"217b0d35d11333f328a59edc04c8412bed24c9ad","tid":1132840,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"幾好 快啲報名參加全民造星二"},{"pid":"98d7991b172a08fc8c1cc08e2b8ab68479d58464","tid":1132840,"uid":128921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:09:50.000Z","msg":"btw樓豬條脷可唔可以落返嚟"},{"pid":"79fe6598343176a580bad497b45c76b302821c23","tid":1132840,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab98cbd7972b7a0d293e01461da282d65ec6faff","tid":1132840,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"想問呢幾個月學左啲乜<br />\n樓主你似係發聲問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"Agger，一低音啲就失聲咁樓下有CM講咗<br />\n仲有樓主學緊唱歌但有啲位又想用自己唱法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且係唱得唔好，都係乖乖跟返CD唱法唱熟晒，自己唱功OK先搞咁多嘢啦(如果係認真)<br />\n利申：唱歌唔好聽，不過呢首以前唱落OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(難聽入面無咁難聽)"},{"pid":"283834b75046e27b6dbe0bb2dd657d5187a0f0dc","tid":1132840,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"正常人都唔會用咩全民k歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724c9e175a43476bfe990cef2c67d0561885f195","tid":1132840,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"中音ok la"},{"pid":"682a93e7b562f9dc38a475e7f70bede888670326","tid":1132840,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"放棄啦"},{"pid":"79a0e2f5e6324d205fbaa6d72b3af7fc18b8ab0a","tid":1132840,"uid":7948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"咬字 條脷 嘴型唔自然<br />\n聲帶控制ok 但氣流唔穩令到件事飄<br />\n初學一兩個月無乜進展都正常<br />\n唱歌講求長年練習<br />\n自己鍾意咪繼續囉<br />\n<br />\nbtw k乜撚野歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb45368f65f6330fe4b29de9729aebc25fbbccec","tid":1132840,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"真心 世界冇任何一個人唔岩唱歌<br />\n但係樓主你呢D人地講完唔聽，各種道理唔明又懶明，實際不學無術嘅on9，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對</span>唔岩唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n音準繼續飄，無氣無力，假音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我俾左龍子成4位數學費，再不停練習先由垃圾變成唱到歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (仲要未算好聽)<br />\n<br />\n你一D意見唔接受，一秒練聲都冇，一蚊都冇俾過想唱歌好聽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果個洗五位數以上搵名師學發聲真係嘔血啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆你咁撚樣唱K玩下人地都可能嫌棄你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}